title: Left 4 dead 2 full v 2.0.8.0
description:
PC Minimum System Requirements


    Supported OS: Windows 7 32/64-bit / Vista 32/64 / XP
    Processor: Pentium 4 3.0GHz
    Memory: 1 GB for XP / 2GB for Vista
    Graphics: DirectX 9 compatible video card with 128 MB, Shader model 2.0. ATI X800, NVidia 6600 or better
    Hard Drive: At least 11 GB of free space
    Sound Card: DirectX 9.0c compatible sound card



This version of Left 4 Dead 2 is 2.0.8.0 (updated 05 Aug 2011),just install and you ready to play on No Steam servers
